sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler
    participant API
    participant Idempotency
    participant MailSummary
    participant Notifier
    participant Channel
    participant Provider
    participant EmailAPI
    participant NotificationLogRepo

    Scheduler->>API: POST /internal/jobs/weekly-summary
    API->>Idempotency: Validate execution key
    Idempotency-->>API: Valid

    API->>MailSummary: Compute weekly totals
    MailSummary-->>API: Aggregated results

    API->>Notifier: Trigger summary dispatch

    Notifier->>Channel: Build email notification
    Channel->>Provider: Send via transport adapter
    Provider->>EmailAPI: POST /send [JSON/HTTPS]

    EmailAPI-->>Provider: 200 / Error
    Provider-->>Channel: Result
    Channel-->>Notifier: Result

    Notifier->>NotificationLogRepo: Persist attempt outcome
